│ the corresponding SCEV expression.                                                         │
│ 4.  Here lies the error: `getPHIValueAfterLoop` uses the *current* `SCEVExpander` instance │
│ (the one owned by `GeneratedRTChecks`) to expand the expression. This causes the newly     │
│ created instruction (`%iv.1.lcssa2`) to be registered in the `Inserted` list of the        │
│ `SCEVExpanderCleaner`.                                                                     │
